  "sentences": [
    {
      "id": "ch38-01",
      "text": "C'est l'arrestation.",
      "imagePrompt": "Medium shot, eye-level, of uniformed police officers standing in the Franklin laboratory doorway facing the viewer, brass batons raised. The Franklin family stands frozen in shock at their workbench, the splintered door forced open as the focal point. Harsh overhead gas lamps light the chaotic 1931 scene, shocking and invasive mood.",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "the_raid",
      "speaker": "Narrateur"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch38-02",
      "text": "L'état a un but.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "the_raid",
      "speaker": "Pizoni"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch38-03",
      "text": "L'arrestation arrive parce que l'état cherche les savants.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "the_raid",
      "speaker": "Pizoni"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch38-04",
      "text": "Le but de l'état est vrai.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "the_raid",
      "speaker": "Pizoni"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch38-05",
      "text": "L'état arrive au labo car il cherche le sérum.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "the_raid",
      "speaker": "Pizoni"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch38-06",
      "text": "C'est vrai.",
      "imagePrompt": "In the ransacked 1931 laboratory, Paul and Annette stand together facing the viewer, grim realization on their faces, while little Avril hides under a workbench behind them. Paul and Annette's stricken expressions are the focal point. Medium shot, eye-level. Gas lamps cast harsh light on the overturned room, fearful and truthful mood.",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "truth",
      "speaker": "Paul"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch38-07",
      "text": "On tremble ici.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "truth",
      "speaker": "Narrateur"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch38-08",
      "text": "C'est vrai, dit Paul.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "truth",
      "speaker": "Paul"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch38-09",
      "text": "Annette tremble.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "truth",
      "speaker": "Annette"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch38-10",
      "text": "Le monde tremble.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "truth",
      "speaker": "Narrateur"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch38-11",
      "text": "On ne va pas abandonner.",
      "imagePrompt": "In the 1931 laboratory, Paul faces the viewer clutching research papers tightly to his chest, Annette standing defiantly beside him, a police officer reaching for the documents. The sheaf of papers pressed against Paul's chest is the focal point. Medium shot, eye-level. Gas lamps light the tense standoff, resolute and unyielding mood.",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "refusal",
      "speaker": "Paul"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch38-12",
      "text": "Le souvenir est là.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "refusal",
      "speaker": "Pizoni"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch38-13",
      "text": "Paul a refusé d'abandonner.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "refusal",
      "speaker": "Paul"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch38-14",
      "text": "Le souvenir reste.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "refusal",
      "speaker": "Narrateur"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch38-15",
      "text": "On ne va pas abandonner le travail.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "refusal",
      "speaker": "Pizoni"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch38-16",
      "text": "Le but de l'état.",
      "imagePrompt": "Medium shot, eye-level, of officials sitting at a heavy desk facing the viewer in a state office, reviewing thick files on the Franklin family. A wall map behind them shows pinned locations of arrested scientists, the open dossier with the Franklin name visible as the focal point. Brass desk lamp and gas sconces light the room, calculating and purposeful mood.",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "purpose",
      "speaker": "Pizoni"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch38-17",
      "text": "Ça colle ici.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "purpose",
      "speaker": "Narrateur"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch38-18",
      "text": "L'arrestation colle au monde.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "purpose",
      "speaker": "Pizoni"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch38-19",
      "text": "On connaît le vrai but de l'état.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "purpose",
      "speaker": "Pizoni"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch38-20",
      "text": "Le souvenir colle.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "purpose",
      "speaker": "Narrateur"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch38-21",
      "text": "Avril a un souvenir.",
      "imagePrompt": "Medium shot, eye-level, of little Avril peering out from under a workbench facing the viewer, tears streaming down her face, Darwin meowing beside her. Her parents are led away through the closing door behind them. Avril's tearful face framed beneath the table edge is the focal point. Fading gas lamp light, devastating and sorrowful mood.",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "memory",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
